quests.desc: Who's got a virtual machine and is about to play through an life changing round of TextWorld? You do! First stop, make an attempt to travel west. Then, attempt to go to the south. Following that, venture west. That done, venture west. With that over with, go north. With that done, go west. And then, lift the fondue from the floor of the sauna. With the fondue, take a trip south. And then, travel east. After that, rest the fondue on the couch within the playroom. Got that? Good!

main_quest.desc: I hope you're ready to go into rooms and interact with objects, because you've just entered TextWorld! Here is how to play! Your first objective is to take a trip west.
